tip.text: Lava cake me cherries kai pagoto pistachio
Egg Benedict with yogurt and butter... And bread soldiers
One of my fave restaurant in bratislava. Good burger and half boneless chicken. The meat:steaks are very good! The chicken caesar is amazing! Potato gratin is really good.
Lovely soy latte!!! Try the red velvet cake.. Very nice!
Try their club and the marzipan torte! Quite expensive for bratislava. Environment is very nice. Feels like you are in vienna
If you get the cake away you have discount..
Try the mulled wine, the duck with cabbage and the potato dumplings!!! Also the soup inside the bread looks very interesting...
Ricotta ravioli and spinach, try pesto rosso!!!!!! Is amazing. Salad is very fresh as well!
New York lemonade is amazing. Cappuccino is so good as well. Good latte.
Duck with Chinese mushrooms and bamboo!!!!
My fave restaurant!!💕❤️💕❤️💕💕amazinggggg thai...expensive but sooooo good... My favorite place to eat every time i am in Budapest!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Very good.. Good quality! Rich chocolate..
Απο φαγητο ολα τα πιατα βρισκονται σε επιπεδο πρωτευουσας! Το burger με καραμελωμενα κρεμμυδια και το σουφλε καραμελας ειναι εναλαγες των κλασικων πιατων που πρεπει να δοκιμασεις. Ολα τελεια!!!
The hazelnut cake is a must if you like plaisir sucre from laduree.You MUST to try the chocolate muffin.. By far the best choco muffin. The rainbow cake is interesting(buttercream with orange zest)
Milky tea with no sugar and aloe vera!!!!!!!!!! Healthy and amazing!! Koi is the best bubble tea company!
Caesar with chicken and poached egg
Great burger and caesar salad. The best choice is the steak sandwich and the fries( contain garlic).
For dessert chocolate cake is pretty good but be prepared.. Is just a chocolate cake with a chocolate sauce and ice cream
Fovero to burger tous! To protimo apo kanonika burger kai as min eimai vegan! Zen tempeh telio alla ligo vari.. Carrot cake kai chocolate tart aksizoun!
Ena apo ta kalitera zaxaroplastia tis elladas! Oti dokimasa aksizi.. Tarta vanillia, sokolatina, pasta fountoukiou!!!! Kai karamelas!!!! 😋❤️👍💪✌
